             <https://w3id.org/TD-Universe/fluxnova-bpmn-model/fluxnova_bpmn_model_bpmndi/MessageVisibleKind#non_initiating> ] ? ;
          fluxnova_bpmn_model_bpmndi:bpmn_label @fluxnova_bpmn_model_bpmndi:BpmnLabel ?
